<br>
&quot;Oh how I have missed you! And indeed, I have been gone too long!&quot;<br>
<br>
Suddenly, a mischeivious gleam came over Yakut's green eyes...the surprise was still waiting outside. She would not speak of it yet though.<br>
<br>
&quot;How have you been, M'Queen?&quot;  <p>-|-Queen Yakut-|-<br>
